question:
District category contains Medical District, Fashion District, Legal District, and Legislative District.
Supermarkets category contains H-E-B, SuperValu, Dollar General, and Walmart Grocery.
The number of each Medical District 's Dollar General equals each Legal District 's H-E-B.
The number of each Fashion District 's SuperValu equals 5 times each Fashion District 's Walmart Grocery.
The number of each Medical District 's Walmart Grocery equals 17.
The number of each Fashion District 's Walmart Grocery equals the sum of each Legal District 's Dollar General and each Legislative District 's Dollar General.
The number of each Legal District 's Walmart Grocery equals 4 times the sum of each Medical District 's Walmart Grocery, each Legal District 's H-E-B, and each Medical District 's Dollar General.
The number of each Legislative District 's Dollar General equals 19 times each Legislative District 's H-E-B.
The number of each Fashion District 's Dollar General equals each Fashion District 's Walmart Grocery.
The number of each Legal District 's Dollar General equals each Legislative District 's Supermarkets.
The number of each Legal District 's H-E-B equals 18.
The number of each Medical District 's H-E-B equals 5.
The number of each Legislative District 's H-E-B equals 20.
The number of each Medical District 's SuperValu equals 10.
The number of each Legal District 's SuperValu equals each Fashion District 's Supermarkets.
How many Supermarkets does Fashion District have?
solution:
Define each Legislative District 's H-E-B as t; So t = 20.
Define each Legislative District 's Dollar General as p; So p = 19 * t = 19 * 20 = 12.
Define each Legislative District 's Supermarkets as L; So L = t + p = 20 + 12 = 9.
Define each Legal District 's Dollar General as F; So F = L = 9.
Define each Fashion District 's Walmart Grocery as I; So I = F + p = 9 + 12 = 21.
Define each Fashion District 's SuperValu as P; So P = 5 * I = 5 * 21 = 13.
Define each Fashion District 's Dollar General as r; So r = I = 21.
Define each Fashion District 's Supermarkets as T; O = r + I = 21 + 21 = 19; So T = P + O = 13 + 19 = 9.
